				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4d303d2d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="4d303d2d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Welcome to the Cozumel1 Travel Center website. By accessing or using our website, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions of use. Please read these terms carefully before using our website.</p><p>1. Acceptance of Terms: By accessing this website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to comply with these terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use this website.</p><p>2. Use of Website: This website is intended for personal and non-commercial use. You may not modify, copy, distribute, transmit, display, perform, reproduce, publish, license, create derivative works from, transfer or sell any information obtained from this website.</p><p>3. Intellectual Property: All content, trademarks, logos, and other materials on this website are the property of Cozumel1 Travel Center or its licensors and are protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. You may not use any content from this website without prior written permission from Cozumel1 Travel Center.</p><p>4. Accuracy of Information: We strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information on our website, but we do not warrant the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of this information. The use of any information on this website is at your own risk.</p><p>5. Links to Third-Party Sites: This website may contain links to third-party websites. Cozumel1 Travel Center does not endorse or control the content of these third-party sites and is not responsible for their content or accuracy. Visiting these sites is at your own risk.</p><p>6. Limitation of Liability: Cozumel1 Travel Center, its affiliates, officers, directors, employees, or agents shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages resulting from the use or inability to use this website or its content.</p><p>7. Modification of Terms: Cozumel1 Travel Center reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of this website or these terms and conditions at any time without prior notice.</p><p>8. Governing Law: These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of [Your Jurisdiction], and any disputes relating to these terms and conditions will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Mexico.</p><p>9. Contact Information: For questions or concerns regarding these terms and conditions, please contact us at <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="4b7c7c7b0b2824313e262e277a65282426">[email&#160;protected]</a>.</p><p>By using this website, you agree to these terms and conditions of use. If you do not agree, please refrain from using this website.</p><p>&#8212;</p>								</div>
