				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Cozumel1 Travel Center understands the unpredictability of travel circumstances. In cases where a tour is canceled solely due to the closure of the port by the governing authority, preventing water activities in the Marine Park, a refund will be issued.</p><p>We appreciate your understanding and cooperation regarding our refund policy.</p><p>This policy is effective as of Jan 7th, 2024 and may undergo updates or revisions without prior notice.</p>								</div>
